post_top_tie_icon\" target=\"_self\" href=\"#post_comment_area\" title=\"快速发贴\"></a>\n                        <a class=\"post_top_tie_count js-tielink js-tiejoincount\" href=\"#\" title=\"点击查看跟贴\">0</a>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"post_top_share\">\n                        <span class=\"post_top_share_title\">分享至</span>\n                        <ul class=\"post_share\">\n                            <li class=\"share_weixin js_weixin\">\n                                <a href=\"javascript:;\" target=\"_self\"><i title=\"分享到微信\"></i></a>\n                            </li>\n                            <li class=\"share_weibo js_share\" data-type=\"weibo\">\n                                <a href=\"javascript:;\" target=\"_self\"><i title=\"分享到新浪微博\"></i></a>\n                            </li>\n                            <li class=\"share_qzone js_share\" data-type=\"qzone\">\n                                <a href=\"javascript:;\" target=\"_self\"><i title=\"分享到QQ空间\"></i></a>\n                            </li>\n                        </ul>\n                        <div class=\"js_qrcode_wrap hidden\" id=\"js_qrcode_top\">\n                            <div class=\"js_qrcode_arr\"></div>\n                            <a href=\"javascript:;\" target=\"_self\" class=\"js_qrcode_close\" title=\"关闭\"></a>\n                            <div class=\"js_qrcode_img js_share_qrcode\"></div>\n                            <p>用微信扫码二维码</p>\n                            <p>分享至好友和朋友圈</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <!-- 摘要 核心提示 -->\n                \n                \n                \n                <!-- 正文 -->\n                \n                <div class=\"post_body\">\n                    \n                    <p class=\"otitle\">\n                        （原标题：安徽：对全省所有大米生产经营者立即开展假香米问题专项排查）\n                    </p>\n                    \n                    <p>@安徽市场监管 微博3月16日消息，为保障人民群众身体健康和生命安全，维护公平竞争的市场秩序，针对央视2023年“3·15”晚会曝光的安徽省三家大米生产企业制售假香米的问题，省市场监管局迅速行动，连夜下发排查通知，并于3月16日上午召开假香米问题专项排查工作任务部署视频会议，布置各地市场监管部门对全省所有大米生产经营者立即开展假香米问题专项排查。</p><p>专项排查对“3·15”晚会曝光的合肥、淮南三家大米企业生产的假香米开展市场清查，消除安全隐患；对所有大米生产企业和小作坊开展全覆盖检查，排查生产者是否持有有效食品生产许可证和小作坊登记证、环境卫生是否符合要求、是否存在以普通大米假冒香米情形、是否存在添加香精违法行为、是否存在虚假标识和虚假宣传等行为。</p><p>对清查、排查中发现生产经营者涉嫌存在相关违法行为的，一律立即采取下架封存、停止销售、召回等措施，强化追根溯源，确保问题产品不再流入市场。同时督促大米生产企业和小作坊全面开展自查自纠、全面开展不添加香精承诺。</p><p class=\"f_center\"><img onerror=\"javascript:this.style.opacity = 0;\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-focus\" src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2023%2F0316%2Fc828bd8fj00rrlmnq002oc000fl00awc.jpg&amp;thumbnail=660x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" style=\"\"></p>\n                    <div style=\"height: 0px;overflow:hidden;\"><img src=\"https://static.ws.126.net/163/f2e/product/post_nodejs/static/logo.png\"></div>\n                </div>\n                <!-- 相关 -->\n                \n                \n                \n                <div class=\"related_article related_special\">\n                    <div class=\"related_article_wrap\">\n                        <div class=\"related_article_title\" data-sid=\"S1678790167573\">延伸阅读</div>\n                        <ul class=\"related_article_list\">\n                            \n                            \n                            <li class=\"related_article_item\">\n                                <a href=\"https://www.163.com/news/article/HVVC9AJS0001899N.html?f=relatedArticle\">315曝光破解版APP违法行为 工信部回应</a>\n                            </li>\n                            \n                            \n                            <li class=\"related_article_item\">\n                                <a href=\"https://www.163.com/news/article/HVVELSAO0001899N.html?f=relatedArticle\">315晚会曝光\"直播间水军泛滥\" 浙江嘉兴查封涉事企业</a>\n                            </li>\n                            \n                            \n                            <li class=\"related_article_item\">\n                                <a href=\"https://www.163.com/news/article/HVUP5GO80001899O.html?f=relatedArticle\">315曝光景区称暂不整改 官方：停业整顿</a>\n                            </li>\n                            \n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <!-- 作者 来源 -->\n                \n                <div class=\"post_author\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.163.com/\"><img src=\"https://static.ws.126.net/cnews/css13/img/end_news.png\" alt=\"柳妙\" width=\"13\" height=\"12\" class=\"icon\"></a>\n                    \n                    本文来源：界面新闻\n                    \n                    \n                    责任编辑：\n                    柳妙_NB24319\n                </div>\n                <!-- 文末广告 -->\n                \n                <!-- 声明 -->\n                \n                \n                <!-- 分页 -->\n                \n                \n                \n                <!-- 跟贴 -->\n                <script>\n                    var isShowComments = true;\n                </script>\n                                \n                <!-- 02通栏 -->\n                <div class=\"post_columnad_mid\" data-adid=\"article_cms_column_2\">\n                    <div style=\"position:relative;\">\n<a href=\"http://gb.corp.163.com/gb/legal.html\" class=\"ad_hover_href\"></a>\n<!-- 广告位：网易-内容频道-文章页面-01通栏 -->\n<div id=\"ssp_7365612\"></div>\n<script>\n(function() {\n    (window.slotbydup=window.slotbydup || []).push({\n        id: \'7365612\',\n        container: \'ssp_7365612\',\n        size: \'600,180\',\n        display: \'inlay-fix\',\n        async: true\n    });\n})();\n</script>\n<script async src=\"//dup.baidustatic.com/js/os.js\"></script>\n</div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://static.ws.126.net/163/f2e/tie-sdk/tie-2020-01137853cb03e8a18f09.css\">\n<script src=\"https://urswebzj.nosdn.127.net/